content: Absolutely great app. I really didn't need the features of the pro version, but I wanted to support the developer. Thank you so much for keeping this project open source. My purchase is the least I could do to thank you for a decision that so few make nowadays, yet it's a decision that is monumentally important. You deserve what I paid a thousand times over. Thank you for this app and thank you for keeping it open source.
replyContent: Thank you for feedback! If you have any ideas how to improve the app please write me on mikhail.kulesh@gmail.com. Happy new year!

content: Excellent app. Have been using the free version for a year and the added benifits of customising the layout and disabling extra tabs and buttons with this paid version are well worth it.
